item.title: Привіт, світ!
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Ласкаво просимо до WordPress. Це ваш перший запис. Редагуйте або видаліть, а потім починайте писати!

wp:comment.wp:comment_content: Привіт! Це коментар. Щоб почати модерувати, редагувати і видаляти коментарі, перейдіть в розділ Коментарів у Майстерні. Аватари авторів коментарів завантажуються з сервісуGravatar.

item.title: About
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Who We Are?

Our Mission

We are just a group of enterprising people who love to travel.

We dream with all our hearts of inspiring you to do new things and to see the world. Especially good if it happens with our team :)

Extraordinary Experiences

We are ready for changes in the planned route and give you complete freedom as a customer to choose all its components.

If you're ready to start the new year with an adventure, then come to us.

Our Advantages

-readiness for change;

-wide choice of tours;

-photographer, videographer, tour guide will be with you the whole time of the trip.

item.content:encoded:
Services

It's Time to Start Your Adventures

It's time to start traveling. It doesn't matter if you're a beginner or a professional. More importantly, we can discover something completely new and different for you.

http://localhost/myproject/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Осенние-Карпаты_-Черногорский-хребет..mp4
Backpacking Trips

With us you can go hiking in the mountains and completely forget about time

http://localhost/myproject/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Унікальне-диво-Карпат.mp4#t=1
Family Hiking Trips

Take your whole family and make the best gift for you - go on a trip together

http://localhost/myproject/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/серфинг-лучшее-видео-SURFING-THE-BEST-2015-.mp4
Water Sports

Never surfed before? We'll teach you, come.

http://localhost/myproject/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Серфинг-на-сноуборде-в-лесу.-Красивое-видео..mp4#t=1
Winter Sports

Want to go skiing or snowboarding but afraid? Come to the beginner's team and learn everything with a professional coach

Why Outdoor Adventure

We have more than 1,000 trips with tourist teams

  • Experience
  • Reputation
  • Guide Experience

What You Get

We'll give you the kind of excursion you never dreamed of

  • 10 videos
  • 1 000 photos
  • 1 000 000 memories

Explore The Colourful World

A Wonderful PHOTO Gift

Learn More

There are only two ways to live your life. One is as though nothing is a miracle. The other is as though everything is a miracle 

- Albert Einstein

Upcoming Events

Hiking in the Carpathians

Tour to the Carpathians is the most popular tourist destination in Ukraine, which attracts tourists all year round! Velvet mountains, numerous waterfalls, ancient crafts, delicious food, ski resorts, medieval castles and fortresses, wine cellars and thermal springs. A trip to the Carpathians can interest tourists of all ages and hobbies.

Learn More
Walking Holidays

Here are collected sightseeing, active, skiing, relaxing, mushrooming, gastronomic, weekend tours in the Carpathians.

Learn More http://localhost/myproject/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Бэкстейдж-с-фотосессии-в-горах-Каппадокии.mp4

Explore The World

We offer over 150 carefully curated small group photo tours in over 50 countries. Our authentic adventures offer you a chance to combine a spectacular vacation with a wonderful creative learning experience. We blend travel, culture, photography, cuisine and more. Our casual format provides a unique blend of hands-on learning techniques and skills mastered over many years, including our exclusive “The Art of Seeing” approach. Whether you are a beginner, an enthusiast, or a professional, we invite you to join us on a truly amazing photographic and cultural adventure of a lifetime.

Learn More

Upcoming Tours & Destination

We offer you a winter holiday in the form of tours to Bukovel. Bus tours to Bukovel from Kiyv 2021 or by train is a great opportunity to spend your holiday. Ski tours to Bukovel from Kiyv by bus (by train) have always been of interest to people who love ski holidays to the Carpathians!

Learn More
